Presearch (PRE) Logo Presearch aims to build a next-generation search engine that is powered by its community. Presearch funds operations through what it describes as a ‘transparent, unobtrusive advertising system’ that enables advertisers and users to stake PRE on keywords. By doing so, they get to display advertisements on those keywords in the search results. Presearch is 100% free to use and Presearch rewards its users with PRE tokens for using Presearch like any other search engine.
You can download thePresearchlogo on full-version of the page. ]] >
item.title: Presearch
item.description: Presearch aims to build a next-generation search engine that is powered by its community. Presearch funds operations through what it describes as a ‘transparent, unobtrusive advertising system’ that enables advertisers and users to stake PRE on keywords. By doing so, they get to display advertisements on those keywords in the search results. Presearch is 100% free to use and Presearch rewards its users with PRE tokens for using Presearch like any other search engine.
